      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major project or a donor car for parts. While the engine does turn over, it suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a rough idle and noticeable fluid leaks that will require immediate professional attention. The exterior shows heavy wear with visible rust on the rocker panels and fading clear coat, while the interior requires a complete deep clean and some upholstery repair. It is sold strictly as-is; please bring a trailer for transport.",
